Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:09.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My eternal first love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:12.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only I could forget, I would live happily,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:15.51,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but my feet always seem to take me back to that fateful park.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:22.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without her, I am forever in pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:27.42,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can only wish for those wounds to heal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:31.44,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.73,0:00:42.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:43.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:56.51,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, something smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.44,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I put on some of mum's perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:00.38,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:04.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The top notes are from la Bergamote, and the body is Chocolat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:05.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:08.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:15.32,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:17.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:26.72,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:53.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.35,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Lady Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:07.43,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:20.40,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(2000,0)}Shoujo Sect
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:20.40,Title No. 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,0)}1st Period
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 165 0 165 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.90,Signs - Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,70)\fs30}Sparrow's Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:45.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu, will you be taking breakfast today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:46.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get anaemic if you don't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.39,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just drink some milk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:53.43,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, please make sure you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:54.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Your neck-tie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:01.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have that dream again last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:02.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:06.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always the same thing, isn't it? How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.40,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It's just a dream after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.77,0:03:19.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.49,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Handa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:05.37,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 135 0 135 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:05.37,Signs - Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,70)\fs30}Art Room{Arts and Crafts Room}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.43,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anybody in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.19,0:04:42.44,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.82,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door! Open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.76,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:55.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,People will see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.87,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Oogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:41.60,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Help, someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.95,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:03.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard it. A girl's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:04.32,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:12.76,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,A moan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,A voice from the art room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.43,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.78,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, telling me ghost stories at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:27.07,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a ghost but a doll, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.77,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:36.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The bell has already gone.\NYou girls should be back in your classrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.91,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, is the story about the doll really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet now, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:46.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully. If it were a doll, it couldn't have possibly jammed the door like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.09,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must have done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:53.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who enjoys fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:56.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who's into these kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.53,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of a person, that's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you suggesting that it was Miss Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.60,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But look, over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.11,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll give them a treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.35,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Handa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.99,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.21,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it was something to do with the Phantom Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:35.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Komai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all right, could I have a moment, Miss Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.77,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lady Shinobu, I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:52.57,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom Doll, huh?\NSounds like some school-yard rumour to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:57.30,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps. However, whether it's true or not I can't say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:04.31,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The story surrounds two girls, madly in love with one another, who a long time ago visited that very room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.09,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay everyone. Class is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:08.42,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.85,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:16.47,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened one rainy day after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:21.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the girls, or so it's said, was unable to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.39,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No one had ever heard her voice before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:30.87,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only during the couple's passionate embrace that she at last uttered a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:33.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Her lover's happiness had been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,However, as soon as that embrace had ended, the girl began to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.88,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a doll, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:46.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,destined to disappear from this world, the moment she made a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:50.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so as she vanished,\Nthe doll wore a smile upon her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:54.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's sad, but at least I can finally call out your name,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.49,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,she said to her lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:03.06,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}Hence was the birth of the Phantom Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:07.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You must never utter your lover's name in the art room, they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:11.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,For if you do, one rainy day after school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:14.26,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who says it will disappear, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:16.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If your feelings are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:21.14,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,When you say "disappear", you mean she died, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:22.75,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Miss Handa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.52,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:30.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Komai, what was that thing you wanted to discuss with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:43.11,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 165 0 165 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:43.11,Signs - Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,70)\fs30}Short Test
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.38,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,85)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 240 0 240 65 0 65{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.38,Signs - Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,90)\fs30}Can I ask for your advice?\N- Komai Chizuru
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:59.21,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That person doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.08,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,take me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:03.74,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.54,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.05,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.55,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:13.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I try to confess my feelings, something gets in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this certain person just isn't interested...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:22.41,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... How should I put it?\NMaybe I'm just going about this the wrong way. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:24.45,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(530,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 195 0 195 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:24.45,Signs - Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,70)\fs30}Observe cleanliness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried almost everything already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.62,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking into their eyes and saying, "I love you."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Even giving them roses on their Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:36.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I don't think this person hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.33,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 195 0 195 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.33,Signs - Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,70)\fs30}Sakuragi Dormitory
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:44.34,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to feel their love and say,\N"I'll hold you, my sweet."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.67,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But even more lovingly than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:50.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:54.38,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here. First, look at my eyebrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.35,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,They look wrinkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.48,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is that, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm here in your dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.52,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be the case for a level three wrinkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This is level five.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Then is it because the bath is full?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Now she gets it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,These are your mission objectives:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:19.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon completion of your third date,\Nreturn to base and report your progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.24,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, take a picture of the target's sleeping face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,End of briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:26.45,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, you want me return with some eye candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.08,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct, soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:33.64,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you won't accomplish anything if you're not confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Move out then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.34,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hide it from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really hate me then say it to my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:19.51,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly. How can I hate my own little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:21.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and put on some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:28.23,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, I'm hurting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:50.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,80)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 170 0 170 63 0 63{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:50.90,Signs - Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,86)\fs30}Komai Shigure\NKomai Chizuru
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.04,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:13.94,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.75,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay you can go in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.78,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? You're really tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.72,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.19,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind even if it's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:39.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.03,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.66,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chizuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:04.66,Main Font - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:11.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Chizuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.97,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.56,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 165 0 165 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.56,Signs - Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,70)\fs30}Self Study
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you locking up for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:48.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to accompany you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:52.84,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you may need some company after what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:56.92,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I don't believe in ghosts or dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:14:59.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the duty of the Disciplinary Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.63,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Miss Naito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:05.25,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, lock up duty is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to lock this room so would the two of you please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:48.57,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:49.87,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Handa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:58.40,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,For goodness' sake, don't make me tell you every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.41,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.15,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,How were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:13.80,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.67,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,My lips. Did you like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:22.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't tell you to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:26.26,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything you want, so please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:29.13,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,My head just went totally blank when I saw your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:30.54,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:38.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't forgive people who touch my lips without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:43.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll punish anyone who does such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:47.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.94,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(320,75)}{\p1}{\bord0.5\shad0}m 0 0 l 165 0 165 50 0 50{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.94,Signs - Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,70)\fs30}Poetry Club
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:53.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:58.12,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,A graduated senior gave Kirin the key, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:01.46,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're free to do anything we so choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.71,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Want a glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:20.38,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:23.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd do anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.52,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me drink from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:49.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.40,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin, hold her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.16,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin is my servant,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,and she'll absolutely follow my every bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to call me Lady Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What do people call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.31,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya... Feeling aroused, are we? {consider revising}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,This will loosen you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:32.89,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:37.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.04,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.01,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already slipped inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.57,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you become my servant, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:51.79,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you can taste my lips whenever you so wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.21,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy that everything worked out well for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.82,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the picture of her sleeping face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:23.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that person a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.38,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who that person was,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:29.59,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,so long as you love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:16.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Handa, you're here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:18.81,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:26.31,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you had a talk with Miss Komai on the rooftop the other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.33,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:31.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you talk about? Chizuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:37.29,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you've been giving her strange ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:42.17,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of what I said, the outcome would have been the same anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:45.04,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really are responsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.93,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are siblings, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:52.76,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why Miss Komai came to me for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.58,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,How to destroy that feeling of love...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:21:00.03,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,So how did you answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:05.35,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rather than destroying your loved one,\Ndestroying yourself would ease the pain."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:07.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:21.74,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.91,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:26.04,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a sweet scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:29.06,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The top notes are from la Bergamote, and the body is Chocolat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.56,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:34.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling around already,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:37.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to lock this room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:38.99,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:48.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:50.50,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? The Phantom Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:54.30,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see if it really worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:00.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:04.10,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:07.32,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:26.36,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Shinobu, can I join too?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:28.69,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us will get wet, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:33.88,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fad(0,2000)\fnFlorence\b1\pos(134,161)}Rather,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:33.88,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fad(0,2000)\fnFlorence\b1\pos(405,255)}I want to disappear myself.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:40.72,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoko! We're going home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:41.86,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:43.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:47.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but mum's calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:48.68,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:50.22,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.51,0:22:56.07,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:00.27,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yet, there was no "later".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:02.74,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I never saw her again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:05.20,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My eternal first love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.10,0:23:08.70,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If only I could forget, I would live happily,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:11.83,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but my feet always seem to take me back to that fateful park.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:17.25,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without her, I am forever in pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.15,0:23:22.77,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can only wish for those wounds to heal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:27.26,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she does not remember what happened back then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:31.00,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for me, the one who couldn't forget...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:33.02,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was unable to say anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.51,0:23:40.30,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An endless game of hide and seek.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:43.37,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be caught quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:46.18,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:49.61,Main Font,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...before your very eyes.{\i0}
